This directory contains the chess engine JNI bridge native code.

License classification by file:
  - engine_jni.cpp: GPL v3 (partially derived from DroidFish)
      Native chmod/renice functions derived from DroidFish nativeutil.cpp.
      Copyright (C) Peter Österlund.
      JNI bridge (dlopen/dlsym/pipe) is original code.
      Modifications Copyright (C) 2026 Regalia.
      v1.0.2: 500+ lines of dead code implementing the removed
      engine-import feature (nativeLoadEngine / nativeStartEngine /
      nativeSendCommand / nativeReadOutput / nativeDestroyEngine /
      nativeIsEngineRunning / nativeGetEngineEntryType +
      findEngineEntryPoint + engineThreadFunc + EngineHandle +
      EngineEntryType structs) were deleted (25.5KB → 4.2KB).
      Only nativeChmod and nativeRenice remain, matching the
      declarations in StockfishNative.java.
      v1.0.3: no changes — only the rebuilt libengine_bridge.so is
      packaged (the source is unchanged from v1.0.2).
  - CMakeLists.txt: AGPL v3 (original build configuration)
      Note: this CMake file builds engine_jni.cpp which is GPL v3,
      but the CMake file itself is original and uses AGPL v3.
      v1.0.2: removed the `dl` link (no longer needed after the
      engine-import dead-code removal — dlopen/dlsym are gone).
      v1.0.3: no changes.

See the root-level LICENSE-AGPL v3, LICENSE-GPL v3, and NOTICE files
for full license texts and attribution details.

v1.0.3 patch: no changes to cpp/ sources (engine_jni.cpp and CMakeLists.txt
are unchanged from v1.0.2). The libengine_bridge.so packaged in the APK is
the same v1.0.2-built binary.
